  <brief_title>Clinical Trial With MSC for Graft Versus Host Disease Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Trial Phase I / II Graft Versus Host Disease Treatment Refractory to First-line Therapy With Sequential Infusion of Mesenchymal Cells Allogeneic Expanded Adipose Tissue in Vitro</official_title>
